        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-09-13T12:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-09-13T12:00:00-05:00" n="622" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d622">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">701.60D 11/9–1345: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé in Finland</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hulley</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-09-13T13:00:00-04:00">September 13, 1945—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>147. Appointment of Kalla Teodor Jutila<note n="7" xml:id="d622fn1">Until this
                        appointment was made, Mr. Jutila had been Minister of Agriculture in the
                        Finnish Goverment. He presented his credentials to President Truman on
                        November 21, 1945.</note> as Minister to the United States, mentioned in
                    your 503 of Aug. 31,<note n="8" xml:id="d622fn2">Not printed.</note> is
                    agreeable to this Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
